.TH VALKEY-CHECK-AOF 1 "2024"
.SH NAME
valkey-check-aof \- Check and repair Valkey AOF persistence files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B valkey-check-aof
[\-\-fix]
.RI filename
.SH DESCRIPTION
Valkey is a high-performance, open-source key-value data store.
.PP
\fBvalkey-check-aof\fP checks the integrity of a Valkey Append-Only File (AOF)
and can optionally repair truncated or corrupted entries.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-fix
Attempt to fix the AOF file by truncating it at the first invalid entry.
Without this option the tool only reports errors without modifying the file.
.TP
.I filename
Path to the AOF file to check.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
File is valid (or was successfully repaired with \-\-fix).
.TP
.B 1
File is invalid and could not be repaired, or \-\-fix was not specified.
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBvalkey-server\fP(1), \fBvalkey-check-rdb\fP(1)
